{
  "stem": "15694.11",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And to the point-- and on the-- on the 12th day of our-- anyway, one of the end days-- I sort of have to sort of now recoup it again.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I should look it up in my book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My father complained so much that he was taken to a nearby wagon, which was called, again, a Konkan Wagon, which like-- like a hospital wagon, which you could not have found, I'm sure, in other-- in any other train.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I have to mention just one thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that is a switch back to when we landed in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "People, when they open the trains, they was throwing themselves on the-- onto the snow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Many died for that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And from the 5,000 which were in the train, 2 and 1/2 thousand arrived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And what I was, at that time, thinking, envying that they had a roof over their head.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I had none in winter, was a blessing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Because we had contact with the-- with a man who gave us the hot water in the engine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we had to eat and drink.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the others were just dying. 50%, 5 and 1/2-- from 5,000, 2 and 1/2 arrived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Now, switch back to this train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We were not so crowded, as I later learned other trains were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But crowded enough that at one time my strongest wish was to just stretch out my legs without touching anybody else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Because when I was-- when we were sitting it was all right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "When we were sleeping other legs came on top of me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And my legs were on top of somebody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And my father then had to go to this couple of doors-- wagons away, into what they call a-- a hospital wagon.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And at the same time, there was an alarm.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
